title: Ep. 203 - Jihad Bride Wants To Come Home
description:
Today on the show, a woman left the US and joined ISIS. Now she wants to come home but Trump says no. Also, Jussie Smollett has been arrested. We’ll discuss the latest in the case. Finally I’ll explain why Bernie Sanders is an arrogant, hypocritical, morally deranged, communist fraud. Date: 02-21-2019
